dct_title_s: The Bay of Coquimbo from a Spanish m.s. : Port Herradura
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Depths shown by soundings. "Additional soundings by Lieut. Owen Stanley R.N." "Published according to Act of Parliament by Capt. Hurd R.N.
